ModuleParameters.Value: public static class Utilities { public static int GetCutoff(long num, List<Tuple<int,long>> list) { list.Sort(delegate (Tuple<int, long> x, Tuple<int, long> y) { return y.Item1.CompareTo(x.Item1); });  long cum = 0; int bucket = 0; foreach(var item in list) { cum += item.Item2; if (cum > num) return bucket;  bucket = item.Item1; } return bucket; } }
